keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

unmapAll

map i LinkHints.activateMode
map I LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map u LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab

map t scrollDown
map r scrollUp
map o scrollLeft
map n scrollRight
map e scrollPageDown
map c scrollPageUp
map C scrollToTop
map E scrollToBottom
map s goBack
map w goForward

#unmap H
#unmap d
#unmap u
#unmap G
#unmap gg
